Product Description▼▲
It's a new---and more frightening---world in 2021 after millions of people vanish without a trace. Now in a virtual police-state, Graham Peck and his family must deal with overwhelming tragedy as they struggle to survive. Is the radical group called the New Believers an answer to their prayers? A chilling apocalyptic thriller! 320 pages, softcover from Warner Faith.

