Robert Wise - Wikipedia






















 






Robert Wise

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For other people named Robert Wise, see Robert Wise (disambiguation).


Robert Wise



Wise at the premiere of Air America, 1990



